- check whether tabs may be incorporated into .overview file

fetchnews:
=========

- implement NEWNEWS for broken Demon.co.uk servers (Carl Inglis)
- don't supersede() articles unconditionally
- groupinfo wird nach timeout und anschliessendem sigint nicht upgedated!
- wenn connection nicht erfolgreich ist, haengt der rechner
- problems with timeout. If timeout occurs, fetchnews should send itself
  SIGINT.
- starts with an initialfetch (!)
- interrupt fetch every 100 postings and then reconnect, to beat the
  INN configuration
- delaybody only for certain groups?
- articles are possibly lost when incorrectly linked (i.e. if
  /var/spool/news/message.id/xxx/<bla@fasel> is already present
  but /var/spool/news/news/group/name/nnnnnn is not).

